  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a large bowl, mix together the kanten agar, tempering chocolate, roasted vegetables, olive oil, salt, pepper, garlic powder, and onion powder.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a molcajete vessel.",
    "Roast in the preheated oven for 30 minutes.",
    "Remove from the oven and let cool for 10 minutes.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy."
